data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort and convenience in this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence. Located in the Emerald Lakes community, this home offers easy access to Interstate 75 and US-90, ensuring seamless connectivity to your favorite destinations. With over 2,000 square feet of heated and cooled space, and a total of over 2,750 square feet, this home provides ample room for your family to thrive! Enjoy meals in the formal dining room, grab a quick bite in the breakfast nook, or utilize the additional nook for a home office or any other creative purpose. The detached workshop is perfect for storing tools and can be transformed into a versatile space. The attached lean on workshop is an excellent spot for entertainment or relaxation with ample space for tables, chairs with a TV mount already installed! To top it off the home boasts a brand-new roof installed in 2023, ensuring peace of mind for years to come. Call today to set up your own private showing of this home!
